      <preamble>
         <formula name="enactingText">
            <p>The Scottish Ministers make the following Order in exercise of the powers conferred by section 13(2) and (5) of the Landfill Tax (Scotland) Act 2014<noteRef href="#f00001" class="footnote" marker="1"/> and all other powers enabling them to do so.</p>
         </formula>
      </preamble>
      <body>
         <article eId="article-1">
            <heading>Citation, commencement and application</heading>
            <num>1.</num>
            <paragraph eId="article-1-1">
               <num>(1)</num>
               <content>
                  <p>This Order may be cited as the Scottish Landfill Tax (Standard Rate and Lower Rate) Order 2019 and comes into force on 1 April 2019.</p>
               </content>
            </paragraph>
            <paragraph eId="article-1-2">
               <num>(2)</num>
               <content>
                  <p>This Order has effect in relation to taxable disposals made, or treated as made, on or after 1<span ukl:Name="NonBreakingSpace"> </span>April 2019.</p>
               </content>
            </paragraph>
         </article>
         <article eId="article-2">
            <heading>Rates of Scottish landfill tax</heading>
            <num>2.</num>
            <intro>
               <p>For the purposes of section 13 of the Landfill Tax (Scotland) Act 2014—</p>
            </intro>
            <subparagraph eId="article-2-a">
               <num>(a)</num>
               <content>
                  <p>the standard rate is £91.35, and</p>
               </content>
            </subparagraph>
            <subparagraph eId="article-2-b">
               <num>(b)</num>
               <content>
                  <p>the lower rate is £2.90.</p>
               </content>
            </subparagraph>
         </article>
         <article eId="article-3">
            <heading>Revocation</heading>
            <num>3.</num>
            <content>
               <p>The Scottish Landfill Tax (Standard Rate and Lower Rate) Order 2018<noteRef href="#f00002" class="footnote" marker="2"/> is revoked.</p>
            </content>
         </article>
